536
00:31:33.800 --> 00:31:34.760
I guess you will.

537
00:31:36.760 --> 00:31:40.480
Being Kat's boyfriend was kind of
the only remarkable thing about you.

538
00:31:40.560 --> 00:31:43.310
but. Justin. you were my Kryptonite.

539
00:31:43.810 --> 00:31:44.770
Zach who?

540
00:31:45.230 --> 00:31:46.230
[Hannah] Dempsey.

541
00:31:46.690 --> 00:31:48.110
Oh!

542
00:31:48.190 --> 00:31:49.190
Sorry. love.

543
00:31:49.280 --> 00:31:51.320
I'm learning all these new boy names.

544
00:31:51.400 --> 00:31:54.950
and I've dragged most of the old ones
into the Trash icon in my head.

545
00:31:55.030 --> 00:31:55.990
[chuckles] Yeah.

546
00:31:56.990 --> 00:32:00.580
So. anyway. I know you wanted me
to hook up with Zach. but--

547
00:32:00.660 --> 00:32:03.420
But... you're into Justin.

548
00:32:04.420 --> 00:32:05.250
I'm evil.

549
00:32:05.340 --> 00:32:06.170
No.

550
00:32:06.250 --> 00:32:09.420
Hardly. He's... jock crack.

551
00:32:09.880 --> 00:32:11.670
I get it. He's all yours.

552
00:32:11.760 --> 00:32:13.800
No. I would never--

553
00:32:13.890 --> 00:32:17.430
Seriously. I have moved on.
times 2.000 miles.

554
00:32:17.510 --> 00:32:19.600
and I'm dating hipsters now.

555
00:32:19.680 --> 00:32:21.310
He's all yours.

556
00:32:23.310 --> 00:32:25.310
[Hannah]
I was an office assistant third period.

557
00:32:26.860 --> 00:32:29.610
So I knew where you were third period.

558
00:32:34.160 --> 00:32:38.370
[male teacher] All right. so that's just
the even numbers one through 40.

559
00:32:38.450 --> 00:32:39.990
You've got to show your work.

560
00:32:40.080 --> 00:32:43.000
Yeah. you heard me say it:
Show your work.

561
00:32:43.080 --> 00:32:45.120
-[bell rings]
-All right. dismissed. Thank you.

562
00:32:46.920 --> 00:32:48.340
[students chattering]

563
