Whoa!

564
00:32:53.170 --> 00:32:54.430
Careful. there.

565
00:32:54.510 --> 00:32:55.800
I'm sorry about that.

566
00:32:55.890 --> 00:32:58.430
Geometry with Bates.
No wonder you're in a hurry.

567
00:32:58.510 --> 00:33:00.680
-Oh. you have him. too?
-Fifth period.

568
00:33:00.770 --> 00:33:02.890
