Oh. uh...

585
00:33:39.680 --> 00:33:42.810
Coach Patrick assigned the game
for history homework. so...

586
00:33:43.680 --> 00:33:45.140
So. sit.

587
00:33:45.850 --> 00:33:47.060
Uh. yeah. Okay.

588
00:33:47.690 --> 00:33:50.110
You always stand and fidget.
It makes me anxious.

589
00:33:50.190 --> 00:33:51.270
[coach] Run it again!

590
