Shut up!

600
00:34:34.190 --> 00:34:35.360
Don't be jealous. Clay.

601
00:34:36.400 --> 00:34:38.070
You'll fill out. Someday.

602
00:34:38.950 --> 00:34:39.780
Maybe.

603
00:34:40.950 --> 00:34:42.780
