604
00:34:46.160 --> 00:34:47.710
Yeah. pretty much.

605
00:34:47.790 --> 00:34:49.080
-[both chuckle]
-[whistle blows]

606
00:34:50.960 --> 00:34:52.670
Whoo!

607
00:34:52.750 --> 00:34:54.000
Yeah!

608
00:34:54.590 --> 00:34:55.420
Yeah.

609
00:35:01.720 --> 00:35:03.970
-Hey. Helmet.
-Hey.

610
00:35:04.060 --> 00:35:05.770
Can you email me your French notes?

611
00:35:05.850 --> 00:35:08.890
I can't understand Madam Steinberg.
It's like she's speaking German.

612
00:35:09.770 --> 00:35:10.600
Sure.

613
00:35:11.190 --> 00:35:12.020
Ride home?

614
00:35:13.310 --> 00:35:15.650
Thanks. but no. My chariot awaits.

615
00:35:15.730 --> 00:35:17.570
Bye. Clay. See you. Justin.

616
00:35:26.160 --> 00:35:26.990
You guys go.

617
00:35:29.580 --> 00:35:31.290
Whoa! No way! The bus?

618
00:35:31.370 --> 00:35:33.790
Yo. bus with hot girl. car with idiots?

619
