Hey. is that seat taken?

620
00:35:43.180 --> 00:35:44.640
You don't take the bus.

621
00:35:44.720 --> 00:35:48.140
I don't? Well. then.
I guess it's your lucky day.

622
00:35:54.810 --> 00:35:56.570
You clearly don't lack confidence.

623
00:35:56.650 --> 00:35:59.820
