with Mr. Bates fifth period.

624
00:36:00.400 --> 00:36:01.700
You did research.

625
00:36:01.780 --> 00:36:02.610
No.

626
00:36:03.570 --> 00:36:05.410
Yes. I mean...

627
00:36:05.490 --> 00:36:06.740
I don't know. maybe.

628
00:36:07.030 --> 00:36:07.990
I like it.

629
00:36:08.450 --> 00:36:09.540
It shows initiative.

630
00:36:10.620 --> 00:36:14.290
So. could I like maybe
get your number or something?

631
00:36:15.040 --> 00:36:15.920
Or something?

632
00:36:16.630 --> 00:36:18.090
So. I could give you my number

633
00:36:18.170 --> 00:36:20.460
or give you some
fake nuclear launch codes?

634
00:36:20.550 --> 00:36:21.970
I'll just take your number.

635
00:36:22.050 --> 00:36:23.840
-I'll just take your phone.
-Huh?

636
00:36:24.470 --> 00:36:26.800
One. you give me your phone.
two. I put my number into it--

637
00:36:26.890 --> 00:36:28.260
Okay. right. right. right.

638
00:36:35.350 --> 00:36:37.360
