655
00:37:28.950 --> 00:37:31.450
♪ I thought they knew ♪

656
00:37:33.080 --> 00:37:37.420
♪ I'm fickle and slow. and I'll never do ♪

657
00:37:40.920 --> 00:37:42.130
[Mrs. Baker] Hannah.

658
00:37:42.210 --> 00:37:44.420
I don't want you on the phone
when there's homework.

659
00:37:44.510 --> 00:37:46.340
I'm just using the calculator.

660
00:37:46.430 --> 00:37:47.470
[cell phone message alert]

661
