784
00:45:26.300 --> 00:45:27.470
[cell phone chimes]

785
00:45:28.510 --> 00:45:30.890
-[gasps]
-[bell rings]

786
00:45:32.020 --> 00:45:33.640
[Mrs. Bradley]
Okay. everyone. settle in.

787
00:45:33.730 --> 00:45:35.730
-[cell phone chimes]
